    "These principles are, in the words of the authors, a \"distillation of best practice\" in research assessment, allowing researchers to hold their evaluators to account.",
    "They emphasize qualitative expert assessment (including qualitatively evaluating individuals' CVsthe \"narrative/evidence-based CV\" style being increasingly used in some academic fields is an example of this in practice (52)), transparency, and recognition of systemic issues in the process of evaluation.",
